data.description: Looking for a home that's move in ready with a great view then look no more. This 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home on approx. 1 acre +/- is ready and waiting for you. Well maintained brick home with a metal roof, tucked away on corner lot. covered back porch for your morning coffee. room for a garden, outdoor activities, or simply enjoying the beauty of nature, this is your canvas. rural living while still being within reach of essential amenities. Close to schools.
